```bash
# 1. Clone repository
git clone <repository-url>
cd Trading

# 2. Run automated setup (does everything)
python setup_automated_trading.py
```

**This automatically:**

- ‚úÖ Creates virtual environment
- ‚úÖ Installs all dependencies
